examples.en: He prostrated himself at every shrine.
He is completely prostrated by the fever.
The huge increase in gas prices really prostrated the nation's economic engine.
examples.ru: Огромный рост цен на газ поистине истощил движущие силы экономики страны.

examples.en: The natives prostrated themselves before the figure of the god.
examples.ru: Туземцы падали ниц перед статуей бога.
